Achievements track long-term progress across the game using stats you
already build naturally while playing.

They cover areas such as:

  combat
  quests and progression
  economy and donations
  exploration-flavored world activity
  guild-specific milestones

Each achievement line has five tiers:

  Bronze
  Silver
  Gold
  Platinum
  Mythic

Useful commands:

  achievements
      Opens your achievement journal and shows your current progress.

  achievements titles
      Shows every unlocked achievement title and the exact command to equip it.

  atitle <title-id>
      Equips an achievement title.

  atitle clear
      Clears your equipped achievement title.

  leaderboard
      Opens the top 50 achievement leaderboard.

Achievements are meant to reward depth and consistency over time rather
than a single burst of damage or one lucky fight.

